    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example boasts a flawlessly maintained Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a reinforced rear subframe for maximum chassis rigidity. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal power distribution. Meticulously serviced, the VANOS system and rod bearings are within factory tolerances. The undercarriage is immaculate, retaining all original heat shielding and factory-spec suspension bushings. This is a mechanically pure, turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
