    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with original paint that has been meticulously ceramic coated to protect its flawless luster. Inside, the cabin retains that signature new-car aroma, featuring supple leather seats with zero bolster wear and pristine carpets protected by original floor mats. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
