    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it. It's in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
