      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 V8 era. The 4.0L naturally aspirated powerplant delivers a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox for ultimate driver engagement. Mechanically flawless, it features a factory-spec variable M differential lock and an impeccably preserved chassis with zero subframe fatigue. Preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service have been performed, ensuring peak longitudinal and lateral performance. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel.",
